               <head>Two collections of letters relating to the Nizam of Hydrabad and Maratha leaders</head>
               <msContents class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2005001641 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85100074 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85104368">
                  <summary>Two collections of letters relating to the Nizam of Hydrabad, <persName key="viaf_26017465" role="pat">Āṣafjāh Niẓām ʿAlī Khān Bahādur</persName>, and Maratha leaders. Formerly belonged to J. O'Kinealy. Covers delaminating revealing inner matter containing names and dates (ʿAbd al-Razzāq ʿAlī 1243, Kanada or Telugu text). IOL stamp not dated. 
