                        <locus from="65v" to="105v">ff. 65v-105v</locus>
                        <note>
                           <p>Untitled fragment of an important collection of letters and patitions (raqīmah, ruqʿah, and ʿarz̤ī) written on behalf of the Nizam of Hyrdabad, Asafjah Nizam 'Ali Khan Bahadur, as well as addressed to him by Maratha leaders and administrators (Lala Kubairi or Kabiri Singh, Rao Pandit Pradhan, Uttamchand, 'Abd al-Nabi Khan, Rao Nabaji, Mahdaji, Maharao Janoji)</p>
                           <p>Text written at different angles after f. 88</p>
                           <p>Not dated and lacking colophon </p>
                           <p>Several leaves left blank at end </p>
                        </note>
